        "path: crates/ralph/src/session/persistence.rs:4 :: module docs say it reads, writes, clears, and locates .ralph/cache/session.jsonc.",
        "path: docs/workflow.md:189 :: workflow docs say session state is persisted to .ralph/cache/session.json.",
        "path: docs/features/phases.md:483 :: phases docs say session state is persisted to .ralph/cache/session.json.",
        "path: docs/guides/advanced.md:973 :: advanced guide tells users to jq .ralph/cache/session.json.",
        "path: docs/guides/advanced.md:1129 :: advanced guide tells users to rm .ralph/cache/session.json.",
        "path: AGENTS.md:168 :: parallel worker cleanup guidance still references cache/session.json.",
        "workflow: rg -n \"session\\.jsonc|session\\.json\" docs crates/ralph/src apps README.md AGENTS.md :: showed code on session.jsonc and stale docs on session.json."
      ],
      "plan": [
